Tool: snort
Description: This tool is really good at packet sniffing. It has many functionalities in regards to parsing through many different packets.
Review: snort can do a live packet capture or can anaylize a pcap file. It is able to see what files are being transfered and it can find malicous connections.
Usage: snoirt is able to read from pcap files and this is the command: snort -r <pcap file> . To analiyze the file, the command is snort -r <pcap file> -c <output location.
